Internal test of angle conversion to different data types.
- Original angle: (double) ang;
- Obtaining DAngle::fromDeg(ang).BAMs();
- Casting to unsigned via (unsigned)(ang * (0x40000000 / 90.));
- Casting to signed via (unsigned)(int)(ang * (0x40000000 / 90.)).

